Go big with your congratulations and best wishes for the retiree with an extra large photo retirement card. The picture and all wording on this template are simple to personalize and colors and fonts are easy to change with the Zazzle design tool. Create your own unique keepsake gift that has a giant space inside for coworkers, friends and family to sign and write messages. The navy blue and gold design features a faux foil interior, stylish modern typography, and handwritten script calligraphy. Please note that gold is printed color, not metallic foil. A jumbo oversized folded greeting card also makes a stylish and funny retirement party decoration idea or sign and is suitable for either a man or a woman. Happy Retirement! Price:$40.05
